<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="by-far">by far</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[修饰比较级或最高级，强调数量、程度等] …得多；最：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's quicker by far to go by train.
乘火车要快得多。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Britain is by far the largest importer of tea in the world. 
英国是世界上最大的茶叶进口国。</p><footer>2015 全国</footer></div></div>